easy-rsa|-----handy-ruler------------------------------------------------------|
easy-rsa: easy-rsa (Simple shell based CA utility)
easy-rsa:
easy-rsa: This is a small RSA key management package, based on the openssl
easy-rsa: command line tool, that can be found in the easy-rsa subdirectory
easy-rsa: of the OpenVPN distribution. While this tool is primary concerned
easy-rsa: with key management for the SSL VPN application space, it can also
easy-rsa: be used for building web certificates.
easy-rsa:
easy-rsa: https://github.com/OpenVPN/easy-rsa
